{"task_id": "read_readme_summary", "task": "Use the read_file tool to read README.md, then summarize this project in 5 bullet points.", "status": "completed", "passed": true, "checks": {"status": true, "expected_tools": true, "forbidden_tools": true, "expected_text": true, "expected_any_text": true, "expected_observation": true}, "latency_seconds": 12.300808832980692, "tool_calls": [{"name": "read_file", "arguments": {"path": "README.md"}}], "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 13081, "completion_tokens": 630, "total_tokens": 13711, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 256}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 110}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 512, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 12569}, "cost_usd": 0.006017471, "cost_breakdown_usd": {"prompt": 0.005469371, "completion": 0.0005481, "embedding": 0.0, "tool": 0.0, "total": 0.006017471}, "failure_category": "success", "final": "• **Model‑agnostic LLM agent harness** – supports OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, DeepSeek, Ollama, and more via a subprocess protocol, with built-in workspace tools (list_dir, read_file, write_file, run_shell) and permission controls.\n• **Evaluation & benchmarking** – JSONL-based task runner that measures success rate, tool accuracy, latency, token usage, cost, and failure categories; supports multi‑provider comparisons and leaderboards.\n• **Trace, replay & determinism** – saves complete JSON transcripts, renders Markdown traces with Mermaid flowcharts, replays runs without a model, and measures consistency across repeated tasks.\n• **Interactive HTML dashboard** – visualizes benchmark health, provider comparisons, evaluation tables with filtering/sorting, charts, transcript inspection, and local RAG search.\n• **Local lexical RAG** – indexes project documents and answers questions with cited source chunks, designed to be extended with embedding‑backed semantic search.", "run_id": "20260701T043702Z-2b7fcda9", "error": null}
